embed_1.title: 📝 | Rules
embed_1.description:
📜 𝗥𝗜𝗔 𝗦𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗲𝗿 𝗥𝘂𝗹𝗲𝘀 📜

Welcome! To ensure a safe and fun environment for everyone, please follow these rules. Our standard enforcement is a 3-strike system, but severe offenses skip warnings entirely.

1.  🛡️ 𝗥𝗲𝘀𝗽𝗲𝗰𝘁 𝗘𝘃𝗲𝗿𝘆𝗼𝗻𝗲
    Harassment, bullying, hate speech, and discrimination are prohibited. Treat others as you want to be treated.
    → 3 Warnings → Ban

2.  🚫 𝗡𝗼 𝗡𝗦𝗙𝗪 𝗼𝗿 𝗜𝗹𝗹𝗲𝗴𝗮𝗹 𝗖𝗼𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗻𝘁
    Sharing explicit, gore, illegal, or harmful content is strictly forbidden. This is a zero-tolerance rule.
    → Immediate Ban

3.  📢 𝗡𝗼 𝗦𝗽𝗮𝗺𝗺𝗶𝗻𝗴
    Avoid repeated messages, excessive emojis, caps, mentions, or unwanted links.
    → 3 Warnings → Ban

4.  📣 𝗡𝗼 𝗦𝗲𝗹𝗳-𝗣𝗿𝗼𝗺𝗼𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻
    Do not advertise other servers, social media, or any content without explicit permission from staff.
    → 3 Warnings → Ban

5.  📍 𝗞𝗲𝗲𝗽 𝗖𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗻𝗲𝗹𝘀 𝗥𝗲𝗹𝗲𝘃𝗮𝗻𝘁
    Post your content in the appropriate channels. Check channel topics and descriptions for guidance.
    → 3 Warnings → Ban

6.  👑 𝗙𝗼𝗹𝗹𝗼𝘄 𝗦𝘁𝗮𝗳𝗳 𝗜𝗻𝘀𝘁𝗿𝘂𝗰𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀
    Listen to and cooperate with Admins, Mods, and Leaders. Their decisions are final.
    → 3 Warnings → Ban

7.  🔐 𝗦𝗲𝗰𝘂𝗿𝗲 𝗦𝗲𝗹𝗹𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗢𝗻𝗹𝘆
    Only **verified sellers/dealers** are permitted to conduct sales. You must apply for the role in the applications section. Unauthorized selling is strictly prohibited.
    → Immediate Ban

8.  🔔 𝗖𝗼𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝗥𝗲𝘃𝗶𝗲𝘄
    All content intended for public channels must be approved by staff before posting.
    → 3 Warnings → Ban

9.  🎤 𝗥𝗲𝘀𝗽𝗲𝗰𝘁 𝗩𝗼𝗶𝗰𝗲 𝗖𝗵𝗮𝗻𝗻𝗲𝗹𝘀
    Avoid screaming, earrape, spamming sounds, or any disruptive behavior in voice channels.
    → 3 Warnings → Ban

10. 😊 𝗨𝘀𝗲 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗿𝗼𝗽𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘁𝗲 𝗡𝗮𝗺𝗲𝘀
    Your username and nickname must be appropriate and free of offensive or explicit language.
    → 3 Warnings → Ban

11. 🎉 𝗛𝗮𝘃𝗲 𝗙𝘂𝗻 & 𝗕𝗲 𝗔𝗰𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲!
    Engage with the community, participate in events, and help each other grow! This is what we're here for.
